name: Koneksyion Bro Brox - Acid Brox
description:
Acid Brox is a processed development in my graphics series (Image Brox) about the design of graphic icons on the broken image that has been made intentionally and similarized.

When our internet connection is not so good or even lost & broken
it triggers feelings of anger, but stay calm because everything can be relaxed. at least we can see Reptar's Dino running and jumping around like celebrating something, trying to entertain us.
